But notice, please, what verse 13 says,

00:44:40.769 --> 00:44:42.929
the rest of the Jews also joined him

00:44:42.929 --> 00:44:45.010
in putting on this pretense.

00:44:45.010 --> 00:44:49.570
So that even Barnabas was let along with them in their pretense.

00:44:49.570 --> 00:44:51.409
Now, I just love this picture.

00:44:51.409 --> 00:44:54.929
You see, Paul telling Peter he's wrong.

00:44:54.929 --> 00:44:56.730
And you look, have a look at that.

00:44:56.730 --> 00:44:59.449
Look on Barnabas face it.

00:44:59.449 --> 00:45:01.289
He looks guilty.

00:45:01.289 --> 00:45:03.170
Awkward.

00:45:03.170 --> 00:45:07.730
You see, he was caught in the crossfire.

00:45:08.769 --> 00:45:10.929
He likewise was getting counsel

00:45:10.929 --> 00:45:13.489
because he was involved with this.

00:45:13.489 --> 00:45:17.289
So what lesson do we gain from this?

00:45:17.289 --> 00:45:21.090
Except counsel, even from those who we are viewing

00:45:21.130 --> 00:45:23.690
as the ones who were training?

00:45:23.690 --> 00:45:26.969
Don't feel that we're above accepting counsel.

